README for PerlIO::via::UnComment

PerlIO layer that removes comments (lines that start with '#') on reading _and_
writing to a file.  Intended as a development tool but may have uses outside
of development.

Copyright (c) 2002, 2003, 2004, 2012 Elizabeth Mattijsen <liz@dijkmat.nl>.
All rights reserved.  This program is free software; you can redistribute it
and/or modify it under the same terms as Perl itself.

Version:
 0.04

Required Modules:
 (none)

The build is standard:

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install
